《'''贝尔要退出：革命卢西安的克里斯蒂安·贝尔重混'''》（{{lang-en|Bale Out: RevoLucian's Christian Bale Remix!}}）是美国[[作曲家|作曲家]][[盧西安·皮安|盧西安·皮安]]（绰号“革命盧西安”）的[[讽刺|讽刺]][[重混|重混]]舞曲，于2009年2月2日在{{lang|en|[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}和{{lang|en|[[Myspace|Myspace]]}}发布。歌曲利用男演员[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]2008年7月在《[[魔鬼終結者：未來救贖|终结者2018]]》片场大发脾气的录音[[戲仿|恶搞]]。曲中还有其他多种元素，如舞曲节拍和2006年[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]与时任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]支持者争吵的声音片段，营造史翠珊和贝尔大吵的效果。

歌曲发布次日，{{lang|en|YouTube}}的观看次数就超20万，到2009年2月5日已突破百万。[[美联社|美联社]]称歌曲是“催眠舞曲”<ref name="lang">{{cite news | last = Lang | first = Derek J. | title = Batman goes Bale-istic with profane tirade on crew | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | publisher = [[ABC新聞|ABC News]] | date = 2009-02-03 | url = https://www.ctvnews.ca/batman-goes-bale-istic-with-profane-tirade-on-crew-1.366793 | via = CTV News}}</ref>，[[合众国际社|合众国际社]]称赞曲段“琅琅上口”，引发“{{lang|en|YouTube}}式轰动”<ref name="upi">{{cite news | last = United Press International staff | title = Bale tirade becomes YouTube sensation | work = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archivedate = 2018-07-06 | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180706022042/https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2009/02/03/Bale-tirade-becomes-YouTube-sensation/90221233694011/ | url = https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2009/02/03/Bale-tirade-becomes-YouTube-sensation/90221233694011/?ur3=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]]的吉尔·考夫曼感觉曲目仿佛恶魔舞会，{{lang|en|[[Techno|Techno]]}}风味淋漓尽致<ref name="gilkaufman">{{cite news | last = Kaufman | first = Gil | title = You Can Now Dance To The Sound Of Christian Bale’s Fury | work = [[音樂電視網|MTV]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170911163857/http://www.mtv.com/news/2431517/you-can-now-dance-to-the-sound-of-christian-bales-fury/ | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/2431517/you-can-now-dance-to-the-sound-of-christian-bales-fury/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2017-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》认为歌曲“搞笑至极”<ref name="time">{{cite news | author = TIME [staff] | title = Christian Bale Doesn't Use His Words | journal = [[時代雜誌|TIME]] | publisher = [[華納媒體|Time Warner]] | date = 2009-02-04 | url = http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1876761_1876818_1876819,00.html | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190427174018/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1876761_1876818_1876819,00.html | archivedate = 2019-04-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，《[[九號電視網|九号新闻]]》认为曲目在互联网上的成功气势不可阻挡<ref name="ninemsn">{{cite news | last = ninemsn staff | title = A cheeky remix of Christian Bale's movie set meltdown has become a raging online success | work = Nine News | publisher = ninemsn Pty Ltd | date = 2009-02-05}}</ref>。《终结者2018》的导演[[喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾|喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾]]很喜欢这首舞曲并存入{{lang|en|[[IPod|iPod]]}}<ref name="grierson">{{cite news | last = Grierson | first = Tim | title = LA People 2009: Re-Mix Master—Lucian Piane, a.k.a. RevoLucian | journal = LA Weekly | publisher = Village Voice Media | date = 2009-04-20 | url = https://www.laweekly.com/la-people-2009-re-mix-master-lucian-piane-a-k-a-revolucian/ | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | archivedate = 2011-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110629124002/http://www.laweekly.com/2009-04-23/la-vida/la-people-2009-lucian-piane-aka-revolucian-re-mix-master%26page%3D1/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="borden">{{cite news | last = Borden | first = Mark | title = Hollywood's Rogue Mogul: How Terminator Director McG Is Blowing Up the Movie Business | periodical = Fast Company | publisher = Mansueto Ventures LLC | date = 2009-05 | issue = 135 | url = https://www.fastcompany.com/1263246/hollywoods-rogue-mogul-how-terminator-director-mcg-blowing-movie-business | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200731053952/https://www.fastcompany.com/1263246/hollywoods-rogue-mogul-how-terminator-director-mcg-blowing-movie-business | archivedate = 2020-07-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，贝尔自称听过重混，觉得“他们很厉害”<ref name="kennedy">{{cite news | last = Kennedy | first = Jason | title = Bale Moves Past Outburst | work = E! Online | publisher = [[E!|E!: Entertainment Television]] | date = 2009-05-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090523010755/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/the_awful_truth/b123234_Christian_Bale_Jokes_About_On-Set_Blowup.html | archivedate = 2009-05-23 | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | url = https://www.eonline.com/news/123234/christian_bale_jokes_about_on-set_blowup }}</ref><ref name="gq">{{cite news | last = Corsello | first = Andrew | title = A Nice Quiet Chat with Christian Bale | work = [[GQ|GQ magazine]] | publisher = [[康泰纳仕|Condé Nast]] | date = 2009-06 | url = https://www.gq.com/story/christian-bale-batman-john-connor-terminator?currentPage=1 | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110722101440/http://www.gq.com/entertainment/celebrities/200905/christian-bale-batman-john-connor-terminator?currentPage=1 | archivedate = 2011-07-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
[[File:2008_07_Christian_Bale.jpg|thumb]]（摄于2008年7月，事件发生同月）]]

2008年7月，男演员[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯蒂安·贝尔]]在[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]参与拍摄电影《[[魔鬼終結者：未來救贖|终结者2018]]》<ref name="bryant">{{cite news | last = Bryant | first = Adam | title = Christian Bale's Verbal Attack Draws Today's Attention | work = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | date = 2009-02-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170902133500/http://www.tvguide.com/news/christian-bale-today-1002384/ | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | url = https://www.tvguide.com/news/christian-bale-today-1002384/ | archivedate = 2017-09-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="afp">{{cite news | title = Holy expletive! Bale caught in on-set meltdown | agency = [[法新社|Agence France-Presse]] | date = 2009-02-03 | url = https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jaJT1WIl1cyzmCr1nW2LZxdGRZGw | accessdate = 2013-02-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224154712/https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jaJT1WIl1cyzmCr1nW2LZxdGRZGw | archivedate = 2013-02-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。就在他和女演员[[布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德|布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德]]对戏时，[[摄影指导|摄影指导]][[夏恩·赫尔博特|夏恩·赫尔博特]]（{{lang|en|Shane Hurlbut}}）意外走入视线，贝尔非常生气并大声斥责<ref name="bryant" /><ref name="foxnews">{{cite news | title = Christian Bale's F-Word-Laced Verbal Tirade Caught on Tape | work = [[福斯新聞頻道|Fox News]] | date = 2009-02-03 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.foxnews.com/story/christian-bales-f-word-laced-verbal-tirade-caught-on-tape | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180823105549/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2009/02/03/christian-bale-f-word-laced-verbal-tirade-caught-on-tape.html | archivedate = 2018-08-23 }}</ref>，声称如果再犯，剧组必须叫他卷铺盖走人，否则自己就退出<ref name="foxnews" /><ref name="afp" />。赫尔博特冷静地向贝尔道歉，事后继续参与摄制七小时<ref name="foxnews" /><ref name="msnbc">{{cite news | author = Access Hollywood | title = Christian Bale's profane tirade caught on tape: Actor berates director of photography who walked on set during filming | work = [[今天_(NBC)|Today.com]] | date = 2009-02-03 | publisher = NBC Universal | archivedate = 2017-09-18 | url = https://www.today.com/popculture/christian-bale-s-profane-tirade-caught-tape-wbna28984085 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170918143408/https://www.today.com/popculture/christian-bale-s-profane-tirade-caught-tape-wbna28984085 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="bostonherald">{{cite news | last = Inside Track | title = Outburst reveals Christian Bale’s 'Dark' side | work = Boston Herald | date = 2009-02-04 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811111132/https://www.bostonherald.com/2009/02/04/outburst-reveals-christian-bales-dark-side/ | url = https://www.bostonherald.com/2009/02/04/outburst-reveals-christian-bales-dark-side/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | last = TMZ staff | title = "T4" Producer – Bale's Tantrum Was No Biggie | newspaper = [[TMZ|TMZ.com]] | publisher = TMZ Productions, Inc. | url = https://www.tmz.com/2009/02/03/t4-producer-bales-tantrum-was-no-biggie/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-12-21 | date = 2009-02-03 | accessdate = 2020-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221211309/http://www.tmz.com/2009/02/03/t4-producer-bales-tantrum-was-no-biggie/ }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|[[TMZ|TMZ.com]]}}网站很快报导事件经过，起初没有引起重大反响<ref name="sweeney">{{cite news | last = Sweeney | first = Fionnuala | title = Bale's on set rant goes viral: TMZ's Mike Walters explains how they got the tape of Christian Bale's outburst on the set of 'Terminator Salvation.' | agency = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | date = 2009-02-05}}</ref>，但2009年2月2日公布录音后引来大量关注<ref name="bryant" /><ref name="afp" /><ref name="sweeney" />。网站称，《终结者2018》的制片公司高管将事件录音寄给保险公司，以防贝尔真的退出<ref name="foxnews" /><ref name="msnbc" />。

2009年2月6日，贝尔通过洛杉矶{{lang|en|[[KROQ-FM|KROQ-FM]]}}广播电台发布声明，承认行为失当，声称事后两人已通过交流彻底解决问题。贝尔还称，两人当天就在事情发生后继续共事好几个小时，此后又持续合作一个月。他还看过电影摄制完成后的早期版本，对赫尔博特的[[电影摄影|摄影]]功底十分满意。<ref name="bbcnews20090206">{{cite news | title = Actor Bale speaks out over rant: Film star Christian Bale has called a US radio station to apologise for a tirade which was leaked onto the internet, calling it 'inexcusable' | work = [[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]] | date = 2009-02-06 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7875756.stm | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191021040758/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7875756.stm | archivedate = 2019-10-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

== 创作 ==
[[File:LucianPiane-wiki.jpg|thumb]]

[[盧西安·皮安|盧西安·皮安]]（{{lang|en|Lucian Piane}}）发布〈贝尔要退出〉前就以各种讽刺重混闻名，作品讽刺目标包括[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]][[阿拉斯加州州长名单|前州长]][[莎拉·佩林|莎拉·佩林]]、20世纪80年代曾在镜头前发脾气的政治评论员[[比尔·奥莱利|比尔·奥莱利]]，以及[[美国参议院|联邦参议员]][[約翰·福布斯·凱瑞|約翰·福布斯·凱瑞]]在[[佛罗里达大学|佛罗里达大学]]演讲时被警察用[[泰瑟|泰瑟]]电枪击倒而引发全美关注的[[安德鲁·迈耶|安德鲁·迈耶]]（{{lang|en|Andrew Meyer}}）。<ref name="lang" /><ref name="ninemsn" /><ref name="grierson" />

据[[美联社|美联社]]报导，皮安“被贝尔愤怒嗓音中的音乐感吸引”<ref name="lang" />，他一共花费三小时制作这首[[重混|重混]]<ref name="grierson" />。皮安称：“一听到克里斯蒂安·贝尔发火，我就觉得必须来首重混……很高兴大家都觉得曲目很有意思，[[夜总会|夜总会]]都已经开始播放”<ref name="rantremixed">{{cite news | last = The Daily Telegraph [staff] | title = Christian Bale's rant remixed as dance song: Batman actor Christian Bale's expletive-ridden rant has been turned into a dance remix | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | location = London, England | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180122161241/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/4516491/Christian-Bales-rant-remixed-as-dance-song.html | date = 2009-02-04 | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | deadurl = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/4516491/Christian-Bales-rant-remixed-as-dance-song.html | archivedate = 2018-01-22 | accessdate = 2020-08-19 }}</ref>。他还在接受《[[洛杉矶周刊|洛杉矶周刊]]》（''{{lang|en|LA Weekly}}''）采访时表示，希望人们记得他的重混舞曲，而非贝尔的粗话：“咱们都生活在同一个世界，所以我觉得与其记得克里斯蒂安·贝尔曾在片场大发脾气，大家不如记住这首重混”<ref name="grierson" />。

〈贝尔要退出〉[[混搭_(音樂)|混搭]]的内容包括贝尔发火的音频片段，赫尔博特回答“我刚刚只顾去看灯光了”<ref name="ninemsn" />。合唱部分包括贝尔大喊“真他妈让人分神”<ref name="marsden">{{cite news | last = Marsden | first = Rhodri | title = Christian Bale: All the rage on the web – The first clip appeared within minutes – and a week on, Christian Bale's fury is inspiring Oscar-worthy satire. Rhodri Marsden follows the links | newspaper = [[愛爾蘭獨立報|Irish Independent]] | date = 2009-02-09 | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130217180439/http://www.independent.ie/business/technology/christian-bale-all-the-rage-on-the-web-1633797.html | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.independent.ie/business/technology/christian-bale-all-the-rage-on-the-web-1633797.html | archivedate = 2013-02-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和“你他妈到底还有什么不明白？”的片段<ref name="grierson" />。歌曲中的[[声音拼贴|声音拼贴]]包括[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]2006年与前总统[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]支持者争吵的片段<ref name="gilkaufman" /><ref name="lowe">{{cite news | last = Lowe | first = Andy | title = Christian Bale flips out on T4 set: Yes, yes. We know you've heard it. But the remixes are even better ... | work = Total Film | publisher = [[未來出版社|Future Publishing]] | date = 2009-02-03 | url = https://www.gamesradar.com/christian-bale-flips-out-on-t4-set/ | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archivedate = 2018-09-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180925162653/https://www.gamesradar.com/christian-bale-flips-out-on-t4-set/ }}</ref>，合成效果仿佛史翠珊与贝尔争吵<ref name="ninemsn" />。皮安告诉美联社记者：“不知道克里斯蒂安·贝尔喜不喜欢，希望吧。我自认把一些会让他面子上过不去的内容重新加工，变成大家喜闻乐见的玩意儿。”<ref name="lang" />

== 发布 ==
2009年2月2日，皮安把〈贝尔要退出〉上传{{lang|en|MySpace}}和{{lang|en|YouTube}}<ref name="lang" />，其中{{lang|en|MySpace}}页面提供歌曲{{lang|en|[[MP3|MP3]]}}文件免费下载<ref name="rantremixed" />，此时距贝尔骂人录音上网还只过去几小时<ref name="ninemsn" />。上传当天，{{lang|en|YouTube}}页面的观看量就超过20万<ref name="lang" />，并在两天内达到70万次点击<ref name="rantremixed" />。三天后，〈贝尔要退出〉在{{lang|en|YouTube}}的播放次数突破一百万<ref name="ninemsn" />，并在首周超过150万<ref name="marsden" />。

[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]曾在电视新闻节目《[[沃尔夫·布利策战情室|战情室]]》（{{lang|en|''The Situation Room''}}）报导〈贝尔要退出〉，通讯员[[布鲁克·安德森|布鲁克·安德森]]（{{lang|en|Brooke Anderson}}）指出：“……从上传{{lang|en|Youtube}}的音乐恶搞作品来看……（贝尔）这臭名昭著的咆哮会成为今后很长时间的热门话题。”<ref name="brookeanderson">{{cite news | first = Brooke | last = Anderson | title = Actor Comes Unglued: Tirade Caught On Tape | work = The Situation Room | publisher = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | date = 2009-02-03}}</ref>[[安德森·库珀|安德森·库珀]]在《[[安德森库珀360度观点|安德森库珀360度观点]]》（''{{lang|en|Anderson Cooper 360°}}''）称曲目一针见血、毫不留情<ref>{{cite news | authorlink = 安德森·库珀 | last = Cooper | first = Anderson | title = 360 Shot: Crew dance remix – The 360 crew takes another turn on the dance floor with the Christian Bale rant remix | work = Anderson Cooper 360° | publisher = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | date = 2009-02-05}}</ref>。《{{lang|en|Vue}}周报》发文称，“要是好莱坞明星言语攻击他人的话经过重混后放上网，结果一天的点击率就远超任何电影评论网站全年总量，这到头来究竟会变成什么样？”<ref name="vue">{{cite news | last = Gibson | first = Brian | title = Film: SideVue: Termination or Bale-Out for Critics? | work = Vue Weekly | publisher = vueweekly.com | date = 2009-05-21 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.vueweekly.com/film/story/sidevue_termination_or_baleout_for_critics/ | accessdate = 2012-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120728225345/http://www.vueweekly.com/film/story/sidevue_termination_or_baleout_for_critics/ | archivedate = 2012-07-28 }}</ref>

== 反响 ==
据《洛杉矶周刊》报导，《终结者2018》的导演[[喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾|喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾]]已把曲目存入{{lang|en|[[IPod|iPod]]}}<ref name="grierson" />。他还在接受《[[快公司|快公司]]》（''{{lang|en|Fast Company}}''）杂志采访时称：“必须承认，重混舞曲（在{{lang|en|Youtube}}）非常热门”<ref name="borden" />。贝尔在与《[[E!|E！：娱乐电影]]》探讨《终结者2018》时自称听过皮安的恶搞，觉得曲目很不错，“他们很厉害”<ref name="kennedy" />。他还收到朋友发来的另一首重混：“这些人真他妈太厉害了！我实在佩服，这反应真没说的对吧？把本来很恶心的东西变成舞曲，这真太了不起啦！”<ref name="gq" />

美联社的评论认为〈贝尔要退出〉是“催眠舞曲”、曲调很有规律，节奏感十足<ref name="lang" />，还称“事件导致贝克在毫不知情的情况下成为轰动音乐人物”<ref name="lang" />。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》发文称〈贝尔要退出〉是“革命盧西安的天才重混”<ref name="herocomplex">{{cite news | author = Los Angeles Times [staff] | title = Christian Bale's tantrum, the club mix | work = Hero Complex | publisher = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | deadurl = yes | date = 2009-02-03 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2009/02/christian-bal-1.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171124165248/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/uncategorized/christian-bal-1/ | accessdate = 2017-11-24 | archivedate = 2017-11-24 }}</ref>，也是堪称辉煌的夜总会舞曲<ref name="boucher">{{cite news | last = Boucher | first = Geoff | title = Christian Bale, Robert Downey Jr., Kristen Bell and Skeletor, all in Everyday Hero headlines | work = Hero Complex; [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 2009-02-04 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2009/02/robert-downey-j.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170924182243/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/uncategorized/robert-downey-j/ | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2017-09-24 | archivedate = 2017-09-24 }}</ref>。[[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]]吉尔·考夫曼感觉曲目仿佛恶魔舞会，{{lang|en|[[Techno|Techno]]}}风味淋漓尽致，贝尔大声吼出的脏话反复不断，芭芭拉·史翠珊随时回敬<ref name="gilkaufman" />。[[合众国际社|合众国际社]]称赞曲段“琅琅上口”，引发“{{lang|en|YouTube}}式轰动”<ref name="upi" />。

《洛杉矶周刊》称舞曲将重音节拍和贝尔的最佳台词混搭在一起，还令“你他妈到底还有什么不明白？”成为全年最令人上瘾的合唱桥段，从一地鸡毛中淘出少许艺术结晶。<ref name="grierson" />《[[愛爾蘭獨立報|愛爾蘭獨立報]]》认为〈贝尔要退出〉构思精巧、制作精良，合唱段落出人意料的琅琅上口<ref name="marsden" />。《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》认为重混舞曲“节奏威胁感十足，堪称喜剧天才，比‘[[美国精神病人|美国精神病人]]’和‘终结者’加起来还可怕”<ref>{{cite news | last = Wheeler | first = Brad | title = Essential Tracks | newspaper = [[环球邮报|The Globe and Mail]] | publisher = [[貝爾傳媒|CTVglobemedia Publishing Inc.]] | date = 2009-02-10}}</ref>。《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》称，皮安把贝尔的粗话与“动感十足的乐曲”结合<ref name="brophy">{{cite news | last = Brophy-Warren | first = Jamin | title = Inspired by an Outburst | newspaper = [[华尔街日报|The Wall Street Journal]] | page = W4 | date = 2009-02-13 | archivedate = 2020-08-03 | url = https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB123449899678881401 | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803171500/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB123449899678881401 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》网站称歌曲“搞笑至极”<ref name="time" />，《[[九號電視網|九号新闻]]》认为重混曲目“厚脸皮但又讨喜”，在互联网上的成功气势不可阻挡<ref name="ninemsn" />。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》声称革命盧西安将贝尔失态的音频片段转变成混搭和恶搞杰作，在同类作品中名列前茅，很可能成为热门舞曲<ref name="bestmashups">{{cite news | author = The Daily Telegraph [staff] | title = Christian Bale rant: Best of the mash-ups and spoofs | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | location = London, England | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181223160138/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/4539066/Christian-Bale-rant-Best-of-the-mash-ups-and-spoofs.html | publisher = Telegraph Media Group Limited | date = 2009-02-06 | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archivedate = 2018-12-23 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/4539066/Christian-Bale-rant-Best-of-the-mash-ups-and-spoofs.html }}</ref>。《[[剂量_(杂志)|剂量]]》（''{{lang|en|Dose}}''）杂志文章也称整整一周都在这首舞曲的闪耀节拍带动下狂欢<ref>{{cite news | last = Collins | first = Leah | title = The Best Thing I Ever Heard...This Week | journal = Dose | agency = Canwest Interactive | date = 2009-02-06 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-01-12 | archivedate = 2012-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120112195417/http://www.dose.ca/music/story.html?id=f627a31c-8075-4b4b-8a60-1fd6c26a403d | url = http://www.dose.ca/music/story.html?id=f627a31c-8075-4b4b-8a60-1fd6c26a403d }}</ref>，《黑皮书》（''{{lang|en|BlackBook}}''）杂志称赞〈贝尔要退出〉是“贝尔失态（音频）的天才夜总会重混，整天都在你脑中嘶吼”<ref name="garroni">{{cite news | last = Garroni | first = Lauren | title = Links: Christian Bale Remix, Vincent Gallo's Wallet, Gwyneth Paltrow vs. Haters | work = BlackBook Magazine | publisher = BlackBook Media Corporation | url = https://bbook.com/nightlife/links-christian-bale-remix-vincent-gallos-wallet-gwyneth-paltrow-vs-haters/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200617053543/https://bbook.com/nightlife/links-christian-bale-remix-vincent-gallos-wallet-gwyneth-paltrow-vs-haters/ | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | date = 2009-02-03 | archivedate = 2020-06-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》认为歌曲属{{lang|en|[[Techno|Techno]]}}重混，即便愤世嫉俗的人也会喜欢<ref>{{cite news | last = Koski | first = Genevieve | title = "Fucking Distracting!!": Your meme of the week | work = [[影音俱乐部|The A.V. Club]] | date = 2009-02-06 | accessdate = 2020-08-11 | archivedate = 2019-11-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191121002111/https://film.avclub.com/fucking-distracting-your-meme-of-the-week-1798215693 | url = https://film.avclub.com/fucking-distracting-your-meme-of-the-week-1798215693 }}</ref>。《名人咖啡馆》（{{lang|en|''The Celebrity Cafe''}}）感觉舞曲创作过程肯定有大批{{lang|en|Techno}}艺人绞尽脑汗的贡献，很可能促动夜总会乐迷热烈参与并提出听起来天马行空的建议<ref>{{cite news | last = Hunt | first = Kristin | title = A Funny Thing Happened . . . | work = The Celebrity Cafe | date = 2009-02-11 | archivedate = 2012-08-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120806191336/http://www.thecelebritycafe.com/features/24602.html | url = http://www.thecelebritycafe.com/features/24602.html | accessdate = 2012-08-06 }}</ref>。

2009年4月，[[北卡罗来纳州立大学|北卡罗来纳州立大学]][[博士|博士生]]马特·莫兰（{{lang|en|Matt Morain}}）发表[[網路迷因|網路迷因]]论文，评述贝尔失态音频催生的重混作品<ref name="morain">{{Citation | first = Matt | last = Morain | contribution = i iz in ur head, shapin' ur interwebz: Rhetorical transmission, Internet memes, and the questionable application of a neologism | title = Running Head: Rhetorical Transmission and Internet Memes (ENG 798c) | editor-first = Carolyn | editor-last = Miller | publisher = [[北卡罗来纳州立大学|North Carolina State University]] | pages = 12–13, 17–20, 29 | date = 2009-04-27}}</ref>。莫兰指出，这些重混作品比贝尔骂人的音频关注度还高：“与近两百万次播放相比，更让人意外的是重混作品虽因原版音频而生，播放次数却比原版高得多，从中可以看出幻想主题和修辞传播学元素的影响”<ref name="morain" />。[[佩雷斯·希爾頓|佩雷斯·希爾頓]]称赞“盧西安·皮安再度超越自我！你一定要好好听一听。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Hilton | first = Perez | authorlink = 佩雷斯·希爾頓 | title = Christian Bale's Verbal Tirade: The Remix! | work = PerezHilton.com | publisher = perezhilton.com | date = 2009-02-03 | archivedate = 2017-06-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170630105635/http://perezhilton.com/2009-02-03-bale-out | url = https://perezhilton.com/bale-out/ | accessdate = 2020-08-20 }}</ref>他还在自办网站上传随曲目跳舞的视频<ref>{{cite news | last = Hilton | first = Perez | authorlink = 佩雷斯·希爾頓 | title = Perez Bales Out! | work = PerezHilton.com | publisher = perezhilton.com | date = 2009-02-05 | deadurl = no | url = https://perezhilton.com/perez-bales-out/ | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175153/http://perezhilton.com/?p=43196 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120920003353/http://perezhilton.com/tv/index.php?ptvid=48c6e65f81a46 | last = Hilton | first = Perez | authorlink = 佩雷斯·希爾頓 | title = Perez Bales Out! | work = PerezHilton.com | publisher = perezhilton.com | date = 2009-02-05 | url = http://perezhilton.com/tv/index.php?ptvid=48c6e65f81a46 | archivedate = 2012-09-20 | deadurl = yes | access-date = 2020-08-20 }}</ref>。

2009年11月17日，〈贝尔要退出〉与另外四首作品一起获[[美国在线|美国在线]]下属网站“{{lang|en|Urlesque}}”“年度最佳重混”提名<ref name="urlesque">{{cite web | url = http://www.urlesque.com/2009/11/17/best-remix-2009-urlies/ | title = Best Remix of the Year – 2009 Urlies | accessdate = 2009-11-30 | last = Urlesque Staff | date = 2009-11-17 | work = Urlesque | publisher = [[美国在线|AOL LLC]] | archivedate = 2014-02-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140227083758/http://www.urlesque.com/2009/11/17/best-remix-2009-urlies/ }}</ref>，但最终未能胜出<ref name="bestoftheweb">{{cite news | last = Urlesque Staff | title = Best of the Web – The 2009 Urlies | work = Urlesque | publisher = [[美国在线|AOL LLC]] | date = 2009-12-08 | url = http://www.urlesque.com/2009/11/17/best-of-the-web-2009-urlies/ | accessdate = 2014-02-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140227090511/http://www.urlesque.com/2009/11/17/best-of-the-web-2009-urlies/ | archivedate = 2014-02-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。网站工作人员指出，皮安的作品“如野火般蔓延”，已成为網路迷因<ref name="urlesque" />。舞曲还在点击者网站（{{lang|en|Clicker.com}}）2009年评选的点击者奖中入围最新最受欢迎病毒视频，但同样没有获奖<ref name="clickerannounces">{{cite news | last = Miller | first = Liz Shannon | title = Clicker Announces Best of 2009 Winners | work = NewTeeVee | publisher = newteevee.com | date = 2010-01-08 | url = https://gigaom.com/2010/01/08/clicker-announces-best-of-2009-winners/ | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181004232130/https://gigaom.com/2010/01/08/clicker-announces-best-of-2009-winners/ | archivedate = 2018-10-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="latestfavorite">{{cite news | title = Latest Favorite Viral Video – 2009 | work = Clicker | publisher = clicker.com | date = 2009-02-02 | archivedate = 2011-10-09 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.clicker.com/gallery/latest-favorite-viral-video-2009/ | accessdate = 2011-10-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111009154345/http://www.clicker.com/gallery/latest-favorite-viral-video-2009/ }}</ref>。此外，〈贝尔要退出〉还于2010年获[[威比奖|威比奖]]最佳视频重混/混搭提名<ref name="webby">{{cite news | title = 14th Annual Webby Awards Nominees & Winners | work = [[威比奖|Webby Awards]] | publisher = webbyawards.com | url = http://www.webbyawards.com/webbys/current.php?media_id=97&season=14 | accessdate = 2013-03-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130307220615/http://www.webbyawards.com/webbys/current.php?media_id=97&season=14 | archivedate = 2013-03-07 | year = 2010 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="nabwebby">{{cite news | last = Hart | first = Hugh | title = Green Porno, Stephen Colbert Nab Webby Nominations | work = Wired | publisher = wired.com | date = 2010-04-13 | url = https://www.wired.com/2010/04/webby-nominations/ | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181116113958/https://www.wired.com/2010/04/webby-nominations/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-11-16 }}</ref>。

